# Cloudflare Pages redirects — https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
# Precedence: explicit prerendered files → these rules → 404 fallback.
# Unknown routes hit 404.html with HTTP 404 (fixes soft-404 issue).

# Apex → www. Canonical host is www.cornerhouse.co.in (SEO.tsx, sitemap, JSON-LD all agree).
# Must come before path-specific rules so host normalization is the first hop.
https://cornerhouse.co.in/*    https://www.cornerhouse.co.in/:splat    301

# Legacy /journal/:id route served placeholder articles — GSC flagged
# /journal/dlf-camellias-resale as "crawled but not indexed". Funnel all
# /journal/* traffic to the real /blog so inbound links + crawlers settle.
/journal/*   /blog      301

/404.html    /404.html   404
/*           /404.html   404
